            <section label="Introduction">
                <p>Preware is a package management application for the Palm Pre. User can install any package from any of the open standard package feed on preware.org (or any other location that hosts an open standard package feed).</p>
                <p>Preware is the most advanced installer currently. Being the only on device installer that can install application, themes, and patches.</p>
                <p><strong>Features</strong></p>
                <substep label="1. "><span>Install / Remove / Update Applications</span></substep>
                <substep label="2. "><span>Install / Remove / Update Themes</span></substep>
                <substep label="3. "><span>Install / Remove / Update Patches</span></substep>
                <substep label="4. "><span>Update Screen</span></substep>
                <p style="height:10px;"> </p>
